# Licence — Split Architecture

This repository uses different licences for different layers,
following the T(h)reehouse +EC corporate design blueprint (Section 0.3).

| Layer | Content | Licence |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Build scripts, page chrome, CSS | `_build/`, generated HTML chrome | MIT |
| Methodology blueprint | `BLUEPRINT.md` | CC BY-SA 4.0 |
| Authored content | `*/breakwater/`, `*/references/`, `*/essay/` | CC BY-NC-SA 4.0 |
| Templates | `_templates/` | CC BY-SA 4.0 |
| Design assets | `assets/` (copied from cd-rules) | MIT (per cd-rules) |

When in doubt, the more restrictive licence applies.

See the T(h)reehouse +EC corporate design blueprint for rationale:
https://github.com/threehouse-plus-ec/cd-rules
